      <title>Science｜从头设计可被小分子“遥控”的动态蛋白</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/zh/literature/science--%E8%A5%BF%E6%B9%96%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9B%B9%E9%BE%99%E5%85%B4%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E4%BB%8E%E5%A4%B4%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%8F%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E9%81%A5%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD/</link>
